CodeSystem/medical-service-moh.name: MedicalServiceMoH
CodeSystem/medical-service-moh.title: קוד מוצר או שירות על פי משרד הבריאות
CodeSystem/medical-service-moh.description:
קוד שירותים רפואיים , כולל שירותים באשפוז, שירותים אמבולטוריים, רפואת שיניים ובריאות הנפש 
 Codes for medical services. Note that while this code system closely resembles CPT and includes a large number of CPT codes, there are some additional codes that are not covered by CPT and, more importantly, some cases where CPT codes are remapped and have different semantic meanings (e.g., code #28899 has two different meanings in CPT and in MoH codesytem). Therefore, despite apparent resemblance, this code system MUST NOT be treated as CPT.

StructureDefinition/ext-administrative-p.name: AdminParentName
StructureDefinition/ext-administrative-p.title: Ext: Administrative Parent Name
StructureDefinition/ext-administrative-p.description: Extension: The name of a person’s parent, recorded for administrative purposes as part of the person’s demographics (e.g to help with identification). This SHOULD NOT be confused with a parent whose details are recorded for contact purposes (Patient.contact) or as a family member (RelatedPerson). Most systems will use the “father’s name” field as the source of data for this extension. NOTE: This extension replaces the old ParentName extension and is the PREFFERED extension. Note: there SHOULD be only one parent marked as 'official'
